        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Healthy male volunteers; aged 18 to 45 years;

          -  Body mass index (BMI) between 18.0 and 30.0 kg/m2 inclusive, weight â‰¥ 50 kg;

          -  Non- smokers or ex-smokers;

          -  Able to give informed consent.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Subjects with evidence or history of clinically significant disease;

          -  Positive results to HIV Ag/Ab Combo, Hepatitis B surface Antigen (HBsAG (B)
             (hepatitis B)) or Hepatitis C Virus (HCV (C)) tests;

          -  Subjects who have received any investigational drug in the previous 28 days;

          -  Subjects participated in a study with PI3k inhibitors at least once in past year;

          -  Subjects who have received drugs metabolised by CYP3A4 enzyme in the previous 28
             days.
